description:
The Brawler has certainly paid her dues. She has
wrestled The Nightmare, The Goddess
and Vendetta. Now that she's had the mat time with
experienced wrestlers, she can show off to us what she
has learned.
The Deceptacon so names herself because she states
that
people underestimate her
all the time. She is VERY strong and likes to rough
it up. However on Ultimatesurrender,
experience has the track record for victories over
strength and determination.
title: The Brawler (0-3)
